description: Introducing a remarkable 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom condo nestled in the middle of all South Boston has to offer.  Spanning 1167 square feet, this property offers a blend of modern amenities and charm, creating an inviting living space. The open layout seamlessly connects the living area to a dining alcove, providing a perfect setting for intimate meals or casual gatherings. The chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring modern appliances and ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. Step outside to the deck and enjoy al fresco dining or simply soak in the fresh air and sunshine. This condo is equipped with central AC, hardwood floors throughout, and in unit washer/dryer. Perfect for a Savvy Investor or end user.
